`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Concentration
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'concentration'

 Concentration acts as a spell that will increase your Intelligence by 2, raise
your hit roll, and lower your damage roll.  Your hit roll will be raised a
greater amount than your damage roll is lowered.

